{"tha-ap331:0.1":"Therapadana ","tha-ap331:0.2":"Umapupphiyavagga ","tha-ap331:0.3":"9 Pupphacchattiyattheraapadana ","tha-ap331:1.1":"“Siddhatthassa bhagavato, ","tha-ap331:1.2":"lokajetthassa tadino; ","tha-ap331:1.3":"Saccam pakasayantassa, ","tha-ap331:1.4":"nibbapentassa panino. ","tha-ap331:2.1":"Jalajam aharitvana, ","tha-ap331:2.2":"satapattam manoramam; ","tha-ap331:2.3":"Pupphassa chattam katvana, ","tha-ap331:2.4":"buddhassa abhiropayim. ","tha-ap331:3.1":"Siddhattho ca lokavidu, ","tha-ap331:3.2":"ahutinam patiggaho; ","tha-ap331:3.3":"Bhikkhusanghe thito sattha, ","tha-ap331:3.4":"imam gatham abhasatha. ","tha-ap331:4.1":"‘Yo me cittam pasadetva, ","tha-ap331:4.2":"pupphacchattam adharayim; ","tha-ap331:4.3":"Tena cittappasadena, ","tha-ap331:4.4":"duggatim so na gacchati’. ","tha-ap331:5.1":"Idam vatvana sambuddho, ","tha-ap331:5.2":"siddhattho lokanayako; ","tha-ap331:5.3":"Uyyojetvana parisam, ","tha-ap331:5.4":"vehasam nabhamuggami. ","tha-ap331:6.1":"Vutthite naradevamhi, ","tha-ap331:6.2":"setacchattampi vutthahi; ","tha-ap331:6.3":"Purato buddhasetthassa, ","tha-ap331:6.4":"gacchati chattamuttamam. ","tha-ap331:7.1":"Catunnavutito kappe, ","tha-ap331:7.2":"yam chattam abhiropayim; ","tha-ap331:7.3":"Duggatim nabhijanami, ","tha-ap331:7.4":"pupphacchattassidam phalam. ","tha-ap331:8.1":"Catusattatikappamhi, ","tha-ap331:8.2":"attha jalasikha ahu; ","tha-ap331:8.3":"Sattaratanasampanna, ","tha-ap331:8.4":"cakkavatti mahabbala. ","tha-ap331:9.1":"Patisambhida catasso, ","tha-ap331:9.2":"…pe… ","tha-ap331:9.3":"katam buddhassa sasanam”. ","tha-ap331:10.1":"Ittham sudam ayasma pupphacchattiyo thero ima gathayo abhasitthati. ","tha-ap331:11.1":"Pupphacchattiyattherassapadanam navamam. "}